thread.title: David

author: David
title: David
text:
Peter Stratakos and Celeste Tralli are a fantastic team that I highly recommend to anyone looking to achieve top dollar for the sale of their home.
When we approached them to sell our house at very short notice they made things happen to get us an auction before Xmas and ran a faultless campaign.
Nothing is too much trouble and they keep you in the loop all the way.
The result exceeded our excectations by miles due to their clever campaign and hard work.
These guys have the depth of experience you need in these Northern Suburbs and will get you the results you are seeking. Good Luck and thank you so much Peter and Celeste.
